records.name: Planktons Beach

descriptions.direction: Located in Hulhumal√©, Planktons Beach is in a rural area and on the beach. Maldives Islamic Centre is a notable landmark, and the area's natural beauty can be seen at Hulhumale Beach and Full Moon Beach. Gili Lankanfushi Beach and Kani Beach are two other places to visit that come recommended. Scuba diving, snorkeling, and parasailing offer great chances to get out on the surrounding water, or you can seek out an adventure with ecotours nearby.
descriptions.general: The 3-star Planktons Beach offers comfort and convenience whether you're on business or holiday in Male City and Airport. The property features a wide range of facilities to make your stay a pleasant experience. Free Wi-Fi in all rooms, 24-hour security, convenience store, daily housekeeping, portable wi-fi rental are on the list of things guests can enjoy. Guestrooms are fitted with all the amenities you need for a good night's sleep. In some of the rooms, guests can find television LCD/plasma screen, bathroom phone, clothes rack, complimentary instant coffee, complimentary tea. Entertain the hotel's recreational facilities, including boats, canoe, watersports equipment rentals, wind surfing, snorkeling. No matter what your reasons are for visiting Male City and Airport, Planktons Beach will make you feel instantly at home.
